summary: This document details communication methods and addresses for contacting Rolando CUBELA Secades (T/N: Rolando CUBELA Secades), a medical doctor in Havana, Cuba, in 1965. It includes instructions for forwarding letters through AMWHIP/2 and AMWHIP/1, as well as addresses for Srta Ernestina Acosta and Virginia Secades. It also specifies the use of 'Pepe' and 'Luis' signatures for secure communications.
title: Communication Details for Rolando CUBELA Secades
